Package: espresso-casper
Architecture: all
Depends: laptop-detect
Enhances: espresso
Description: Configuration hooks for live installer
 This package provides hook scripts for the Espresso live installer that
 repeat some pieces of configuration done by the live system boot process in
 the system installed by Espresso.
